Project Name: PathWise


Project Vision

The goal of this project is to build a modern AI-powered Career Intelligence Platform that helps users discover the best career opportunities based on their education, interests, skills, strengths, personality, and career goals.

Unlike traditional career guidance websites that only list career options, this platform acts like a personalized career mentor.

It should help users:

• Discover careers
• Discover underrated opportunities
• Discover entrance exams
• Discover government jobs
• Discover higher studies options
• Discover certifications
• Discover scholarships
• Identify missing skills
• Build personalized learning roadmaps
• Become job ready

The platform should not only recommend careers but also expose users to opportunities they may never have heard of.

Example:

A B.Tech student usually knows

• GATE
• Placements
• CAT

But may never know about

• SAIL MT
• BARC OCES
• ISRO Recruitment
• DRDO Scientist
• BEL
• ECIL
• HAL
• ONGC
• NPCIL
• C-DAC
• NIC Scientist

Similarly, Arts, Commerce and Science students should also receive all possible career opportunities including underrated ones.

The platform should function as a Career Intelligence Platform rather than only a Career Recommendation Platform.

